    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Section 1 — Company story (approved copy)"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "story_eyebrow",
      "label": "Eyebrow",
      "default": "About Happie"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "story_headline",
      "label": "Headline (line before accent)",
      "default": "Born in California. Built for"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "story_headline_accent",
      "label": "Headline accent (orange)",
      "default": "Better."
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "story_body",
      "label": "Body",
      "default": "<p>Happie started with a simple belief: what you drink should make you feel good — and you should feel good about drinking it.</p><p>Founded in 2019 by Pete Olander, Happie is a functional beverage company rooted in Northern California’s plant medicine culture. We make two product lines — hemp-derived Delta-9 THC seltzers and Fungi Fusion adaptogenic mushroom drinks — designed for adults who want something better than alcohol and more effective than another sparkling water.</p><p>Every can is batch-tested, transparently labeled, and formulated with intention. Our THC seltzers use nano-emulsified hemp extract for fast-acting effects you can feel in 15 minutes — not two hours. Our Fungi Fusion line delivers clinical-dose functional mushrooms (Lion’s Mane, Cordyceps, and Reishi) with ocean-derived minerals, no THC, and no compromises.</p><p>We’re not here to follow the beverage industry playbook. We’re here to rewrite it — with science-backed formulations, radical transparency, and a brand built on the belief that wellness and enjoyment belong in the same can.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "image_hero_cloud",
      "label": "Hero image (optional)",
      "info": "e.g. happie-cloud.png — layout only; copy is fixed in markdown"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "padding_hero_top",
      "min": 40,
      "max": 120,
      "step": 4,
      "unit": "px",
      "label": "Hero padding top",
      "default": 84,
      "info": "Adds to automatic clearance for the announcement bar + nav. Increase if text still tucks under the menu."
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "hero_header_extra_clearance",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 64,
      "step": 4,
      "unit": "px",
      "label": "Extra space below header",
      "default": 36,
      "info": "Breathing room between the nav pill and the first line of hero copy."
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "padding_hero_bottom",
      "min": 32,
      "max": 100,
      "step": 4,
      "unit": "px",
      "label": "Hero padding bottom",
      "default": 48
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Hero → values curve (same system as homepage)"
